I"b<p>I am an Associate Professor at the Econometric Institute of the <a href="http://www.eur.nl/ese">Erasmus School of Economics</a> and an Economist at the research department of <a href="http://www.dnb.nl">De Nederlandsche Bank</a>. I am affiliated with
the <a href="http://www.tinbergen.nl">Tinbergen Institute</a>, <a href="http://www.erim.eur.nl">ERIM</a>, and the <a href="http://www.cesifo-group.de">CESifo Institute</a>.</p>

<p>Before joining Erasmus and DNB, I was a post-doc at the <a href="http://www.econ.cam.ac.uk">Economics Faculty</a> in Cambridge and an Economist at the <a href="http://www.dmo.gov.uk">UK Debt Management Office</a>.  I have a PhD from the <a href="http://www.cam.ac.uk">University of Cambridge</a> and an undergrad degree from <a href="http://www.wiwi.hu-berlin.de">Humboldt University Berlin</a>.</p>

